      <section id="858f93ad-5e01-49a1-943c-27d7c904cfad">
         <title>Prerecording</title>
         <div id="0cff9e42-bcfc-4b17-b906-0b09bbcc9ca3">
            <p outputclass="title" id="d5c3694f-4af7-4b65-a508-30cec41563ec">
               <xref outputclass="ps_link"
                     keyref="rdaeP20006/95f8ef59-1ee7-4f3a-bdc1-d6dc51de7304">Prerecording</xref>
            </p>
            <div id="1770ebc5-195f-4eda-b3b0-c3bd1354eec3">
               <p>
                  <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/p_pnk_vdh_r4b"/>for the following linguistic content:</p>
               <ol>
                  <li>Text underlying printed music (scores)</li>
                  <li>Sung or spoken text (recordings)</li>
                  <li>Text presented separately (e.g., librettos)</li>
                  <li>Subtitles</li>
                  <li>Accompanying text (e.g., critical commentary, program notes)</li>
               </ol>
               <p>If readily ascertainable, also record Work: <xref keyref="rdawP10353"/> for the original language of printed, sung, spoken, or accompanying text.</p>
            </div>
         </div>
      </section>
      <section id="a90af237-49a5-4da5-9148-8fd60802ad67">
         <title>Recording</title>
         <div id="132804b7-4be5-41ca-bf40-f043e858eb0f">
