               <xref outputclass="ps_link"
                     keyref="rdaeP20006/16b57fb8-9f73-4e10-82d9-f88964388f36">Recording</xref>
            </p>
            <div id="9b991070-6e5c-4b9b-8118-9da36f2c6a56">
               <p>
                  <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_osx_rxr_x4b"/>
                  <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_t1t_rgd_z4b"/>field 008 bytes 35-37 and, if needed, 041 (second indicator blank) subfields $a, $d, $e, $g, or $j. For text underlying printed music, sung or spoken text, and subtitles, routinely also record as an unstructured description using field 546 subfield $a. For other language content, optionally record as an unstructured description using field 546 or 500 if deemed useful for identification or selection.</p>
               <p><ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_scx_vlz_31c"/><ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_lvm_55z_31c"/></p>
